Data Fields

uint8_t * ptrBuffer
 Pointer to the result buffer: Set to NULL implies that the profile does not have any result available.
 
uint32_t size
 Size of the result buffer: Set to 0 implies that the profile does not have any result available.
 

Detailed Description

TestFmk Profile Results.

Profiles post the result of the execution by populating this. The framework does not interpret this and passes this directly from the profile to the application. Developers are required to read the profile documentation about the exact format of the result.
